==English==
===Noun===
'''pavement'''

#(''chiefly British'') a paved footpath at the side of a [[road]]
#(''US'') the paved surface of a road.

====Synonyms====
*(footpath) [[sidewalk]] (''US'')
*(surface of road) [[roadway]] (''British''), [[road]] [[surface]] (''British''), [[pave]] (''US'')

